INTENT
================================================================================

This License is designed to keep the Work non-exclusive and publicly
inspectable while imposing clear, recurring commercial payment obligations on
the largest commercial and institutional beneficiaries.

The reporting, valuation, and anti-evasion provisions are included to reduce
avoidable proof fights. As long as a Top Entity continues to use the Work at
that scale, the payment obligation continues at that scale.

Future versions of this License follow the sequence v7.77, v7.777, v7.7777,
and so on.

